&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proactive owner who takes initiative to build the playbook from scratch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An agile strategist who possesses the discipline of big tech but thrives in the fast-paced, unscripted environment of a startup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
